688
00:33:54,198 --> 00:33:57,733
un mouvement soudain...

689
00:33:57,734 --> 00:34:02,705
une menace mortelle...

690
00:34:02,706 --> 00:34:04,440
gore...

691
00:34:04,441 --> 00:34:07,477
[grognement de créature]

692
00:34:07,478 --> 00:34:09,812
